n</category><category domain="http://www.nytimes.com/namespaces/keywords/nyt_des">Yvonne Gonzalez Rogers</category><category domain="http://www.nytimes.com/namespaces/keywords/nyt_des">Elon Musk</category><media:content url="https://static01.nyt.com/images/2026/05/14/multimedia/14biz-trial-ledeall-1-cmhg/14biz-trial-ledeall-1-cmhg-videoSixteenByNineJumbo1600.jpg" medium="image"><media:credit>Jason Henry for The New York Times</media:credit><media:description>Lawyers for Elon Musk and OpenAI made their closing arguments on Thursday in federal court in Oakland, Calif.</media:description></media:content></item></channel></rss>